  <Dialog id="0" name="MSG_000_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 7 0 202 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 1 0 0}I've been looking for you.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 7 0 202 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 2 0 0}What are you doing here?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="1" name="MSG_001_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 221 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 3 0 0}I kinda just... ended up here somehow.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 221 3 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 4 0 0}{f 4 23 0 221 3 25 25}It's so strange... The sky and the ground look all weird, and there's no one around.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 221 3 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 5 0 0}Something bad's happening right now, but for some reason, I feel at peace.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="2" name="MSG_002_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 7 3 202 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 6 0 0}...Have you forgotten?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="3" name="MSG_003_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 221 4 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 7 0 0}What?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="4" name="MSG_004_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 7 2 202 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 8 0 0}This is the Dark Hour. Ordinary people shouldn't be free to roam about.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 7 2 202 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 9 0 0}But you... You've adapted to it somehow. Too well for a human.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="5" name="MSG_005_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 221 3 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 0 0 0 10 0 0}......[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="6" name="MSG_006_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 7 2 202 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 11 0 0}...I finally understand.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 7 2 202 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 12 0 0}That's why I feel this way whenever you are around.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="7" name="MSG_007_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 7 2 202 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 13 0 0}You are dangerous. You are... my enemy.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="8" name="MSG_008_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 221 3 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 14 0 0}Your enemy?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 221 3 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 15 0 0}Enemy...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="9" name="MSG_009_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 221 3 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 16 0 0}That's right... It was on a night like this with a full moon.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 221 3 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 17 0 0}It was... a long time ago.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="10" name="MSG_010_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 7 2 202 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 18 0 0}Yes. We've met once before.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 7 2 202 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 19 0 0}You and I were enemies.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="11" name="MSG_011_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 221 3 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 20 0 0}Who... am I?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="12" name="MSG_012_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 221 3 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 21 0 0}Who are you?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="13" name="MSG_013_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 7 0 202 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 22 0 0}I am Aigis.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 7 0 202 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 23 0 0}The last of the Anti-Shadow Suppression Weapons.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 7 2 202 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 24 0 0}{f 4 23 0 7 2 25 25}I was created to destroy Shadows.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="14" name="MSG_014_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 221 3 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 25 0 0}Created to destroy...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="15" name="MSG_015_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 7 2 202 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 26 0 0}And you... Your true name is "Death."[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 7 2 202 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 27 0 0}You are the Shadow I sealed away ten years ago![n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="16" name="MSG_016_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 221 3 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 28 0 0}Shadow...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
